    "body": "Problem:\r\nSystem installed sources of Rust standard library are not detected as library sources.\r\n\r\nSolution:\r\nAdd sources location to paths used for library check. See also: https://rust-analyzer.github.io/book/configuration.html#cargo.sysrootSrc\r\n\r\nFixes #4337",
    "closed_at": "2026-03-09T19:47:59Z",
