            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "does this depend on the user's config `settings` item? that seems rather niche.\n\nthis PR really needs a clearer explanation, and possibly doc updates if relevant.\n\nit almost seems like this is reinventing things that cargo or rust should be doing for us. cc @mikejmcguirk @igorlfs ",
